636
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:03,160
[Taichi: Or refreshing... I mean,]

637
00:42:03,160 --> 00:42:05,880
[Taichi: the fresh scent suits you too.]

638
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:07,220
[Taichi: Can I smell them all?]

639
00:42:07,220 --> 00:42:09,560
[Yes, you can.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think we need to smell them all.]

640
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:11,780
[Hmm~]

641
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:15,480
[That's also a citrusy scent.]

642
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:21,280
[Meticulously choosing a scent
that suits the other]

643
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:24,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm done.]

644
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:26,280
[Taichi: Really?]

645
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,960
[Taichi: It's hard.]

646
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:30,520
[The scents may mix
when you smell them consecutively]

647
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:34,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: I've chosen both.]

648
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,760
[Taichi: I've chosen two too.]

649
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:42,240
[Can you tell me one by one?]

650
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:46,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think this one suits me.]
[Oh, bergamot.]

651
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:47,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, and]

652
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:49,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think grapefruit suits him.]

653
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:50,960
[Taichi: Oh, really?]

654
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:53,660
[Taichi: I also chose that for myself.]

655
00:42:53,660 --> 00:42:56,380
[Surprised]

656
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:57,560
[Taichi: For you,]

657
00:42:57,560 --> 00:42:59,540
[Taichi: I chose...]

658
00:42:59,540 --> 00:42:59,690
[Taichi's choice (bergamot)]

659
00:42:59,690 --> 00:43:00,700
This one.

660
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:06,180
[Both of you seem to know each other well.]

661
00:43:06,180 --> 00:43:06,780
[Shy]

662
00:43:06,780 --> 00:43:07,760
[Shy]
[Fascinating.]

663
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:13,920
[Put two or three drops to the palm.]

664
00:43:17,040 --> 00:43:18,240
[Rub your palms.]

665
00:43:18,240 --> 00:43:21,200
[You can rub it into the back of the neck too.]

666
00:43:21,200 --> 00:43:28,560
[Taichi and Han Gyeol apply the scent
that they chose for each other]

667
00:43:31,160 --> 00:43:32,720
[It's aromatic, right?]

668
00:43:32,720 --> 00:43:34,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

669
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:37,080
[In fact, the scent you just picked]

670
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:39,920
[helps you maintain a relatively stable state]

671
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:41,560
[while giving you positive energy]

672
00:43:41,560 --> 00:43:44,480
[and allowing you to]

673
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:47,000
[emit that energy to others.]

674
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:51,360
[What kind of energy will the couples yoga
bring to Taichi and Han Gyeol?]

675
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:55,680
[First, let's do a simple test on]

676
00:43:55,680 --> 00:43:58,680
[how agile and flexible you are.]

677
00:43:58,680 --> 00:44:02,560
[Stretch your legs forward one by one.]

678
00:44:02,560 --> 00:44:05,040
[Can you hold onto the bottom of your feet?]

679
00:44:05,040 --> 00:44:07,340
[Then stretch your legs out slowly.]

680
00:44:07,380 --> 00:44:09,340
[Ah...]

681
00:44:09,340 --> 00:44:11,820
[Ah!]

682
00:44:11,860 --> 00:44:14,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: I've reached my limit.]

683
00:44:14,380 --> 00:44:14,830
[Ah!]

684
00:44:14,830 --> 00:44:16,020
Let's try a bit more.

685
00:44:16,340 --> 00:44:18,580
[Ah!]

686
00:44:18,600 --> 00:44:20,070
[Let's just hold on for five seconds.]

687
00:44:20,070 --> 00:44:20,760
OK.

688
00:44:20,760 --> 00:44:23,580
[Good. You can breathe with your mouth.]

689
00:44:23,620 --> 00:44:25,740
[Exhales~]

690
00:44:26,040 --> 00:44:28,660
[The second breath.]

691
00:44:28,660 --> 00:44:29,380
[Exhales~]

692
00:44:29,380 --> 00:44:31,780
[Exhales~]
[And stretch your legs out more.]

693
00:44:31,800 --> 00:44:33,640
[That's right. The third breath.]

694
00:44:34,140 --> 00:44:36,540
[Exhales~] [Exhales~]

695
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:39,440
[On the fourth breath,
stretch your legs out further.]

696
00:44:41,340 --> 00:44:42,340
[Ah...]

697
00:44:42,860 --> 00:44:44,340
[Ah]

698
00:44:44,480 --> 00:44:45,860
[The last breath.]

699
00:44:45,860 --> 00:44:47,820
[Exhales~]

700
00:44:47,820 --> 00:44:50,320
[Placing your palms on the mat,
one palm at a time,]

701
00:44:50,320 --> 00:44:53,440
[straighten your body and exhale...]

702
00:44:53,440 --> 00:44:57,640
[Guys, this is the warm-up.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: OK.]

703
00:44:57,760 --> 00:44:57,840
Lower your body slowly for 3 seconds.

704
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:00,800
[The warm-up is getting harder]

705
00:45:02,580 --> 00:45:04,940
[Ah... Ugh]

706
00:45:05,700 --> 00:45:06,560
Flat on the mat.

707
00:45:07,120 --> 00:45:09,760
[Woah! Both of you have persisted.]
[Ah...]

708
00:45:10,380 --> 00:45:12,020
[Wow.] [Ah.]

709
00:45:12,040 --> 00:45:13,920
[Taichi: How far are you going?]
[Our goal is...]

710
00:45:13,920 --> 00:45:16,300
[for Taichi's elbows to touch the ground.]

711
00:45:16,340 --> 00:45:17,340
[What?]

712
00:45:17,340 --> 00:45:20,340
[Ah!]

713
00:45:20,340 --> 00:45:21,800
[Ah!]
[Taichi: Is this possible?]

714
00:45:21,800 --> 00:45:26,600
[Your elbows should touch the ground.]

715
00:45:26,600 --> 00:45:29,760
[Bend down until you touch the mat.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: The mat?]

716
00:45:29,760 --> 00:45:31,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: See how you like it now.]

717
00:45:31,280 --> 00:45:31,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: Have a taste!]

718
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:34,840
[Taichi: Ah, really! Wait.]

719
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:37,200
[Kim Han Gyeol: I touched it.]
[Hold for 3 seconds. Good.]

720
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:38,890
The second second.

721
00:45:40,240 --> 00:45:42,800
[Get up really slowly.]

722
00:45:42,800 --> 00:45:43,680
[This process is also important.]

723
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:45,750
Get up slowly. Slowly.

724
00:45:46,740 --> 00:45:48,260
[Shaking]

725
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:52,680
[Release your hands,
put them on the knees, and breathe.]

726
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:54,300
[Exhales~]

727
00:45:54,300 --> 00:45:55,620
[Exhales~]
[Is it doable?]

728
00:45:55,620 --> 00:45:57,620
[Glaring]

729
00:45:57,620 --> 00:46:00,280
[All wiped out.]

730
00:46:00,280 --> 00:46:02,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's more intense than I thought.]
[Taichi: Yeah!]

731
00:46:04,040 --> 00:46:06,960
[You can open wider.]

732
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:11,040
[Taichi: Isn't this a punishment?]

733
00:46:11,040 --> 00:46:12,100
[Good.]

734
00:46:12,100 --> 00:46:13,130
So far so good?

735
00:46:13,130 --> 00:46:15,770
Now, sit up straight while breathing in.

736
00:46:16,200 --> 00:46:18,240
[Ugh... Ah!]
[And exhale.]

737
00:46:18,240 --> 00:46:20,760
[Push your legs out slowly.]

738
00:46:21,720 --> 00:46:23,280
[Ah!]
[Great job.]

739
00:46:23,280 --> 00:46:25,280
[What do you think of each other's flexibility?]

740
00:46:25,280 --> 00:46:26,880
[Taichi: I think I'm more flexible than him.]

741
00:46:26,880 --> 00:46:30,680
[Oh? Seriously?]

742
00:46:30,680 --> 00:46:31,800
[Let's start the third level.]

743
00:46:32,280 --> 00:46:35,240
[Slowly reach your legs out toward the ceiling.]

744
00:46:37,120 --> 00:46:38,800
[Good! Good!]

745
00:46:39,320 --> 00:46:41,640
[You're doing great. Can you raise your head?]

746
00:46:41,640 --> 00:46:42,880
[Make eye contact.]

747
00:46:42,880 --> 00:46:44,360
[Let's... Good.]

748
00:46:44,360 --> 00:46:46,280
[With a gentle gaze.]

749
00:46:46,280 --> 00:46:49,240
[Taichi: Gentle...]

750
00:46:49,240 --> 00:46:50,400
[Take two breaths here.]

751
00:46:50,400 --> 00:46:52,720
[Raise your head when breathing.]

752
00:46:54,080 --> 00:46:56,880
[Kim Han Gyeol: Doing yoga together alone]

753
00:46:56,880 --> 00:47:00,120
[Kim Han Gyeol: was novel but awkward.]

754
00:47:00,120 --> 00:47:01,760
[Kim Han Gyeol:
The instructor said to make eye contact,]

755
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:04,600
[Kim Han Gyeol: but we were both out of breath.]

756
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:06,600
[Kim Han Gyeol: So it wasn't very romantic.]

757
00:47:06,600 --> 00:47:10,760
[Kim Han Gyeol:
And I'm not that close to Taichi.]

758
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:15,040
[Kim Han Gyeol: Being interested in each other
and being close are different,]

759
00:47:15,040 --> 00:47:18,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: so it was a little awkward.]

760
00:47:18,960 --> 00:47:21,200
[Hug each other again.]

761
00:47:21,560 --> 00:47:21,750
[Concealed feelings
as they carry on with the couples yoga]

762
00:47:21,750 --> 00:47:24,280
Let's make a little tree right away this time.

763
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:27,520
[Stretch your hands up.]

764
00:47:28,320 --> 00:47:31,480
[Touch palms above your heads.]

765
00:47:31,480 --> 00:47:32,680
[That's right.]

766
00:47:32,680 --> 00:47:35,160
[Stretch your body upwards.]

767
00:47:35,160 --> 00:47:36,440
[Good job.]

768
00:47:36,440 --> 00:47:37,920
[Hold for two seconds.]

769
00:47:37,920 --> 00:47:42,120
[One, stretch your arm out
and put it down slowly.]

770
00:47:42,120 --> 00:47:43,280
[Exhale.]

771
00:47:43,680 --> 00:47:45,840
[Great. Let's flow into the next move.]

772
00:47:45,840 --> 00:47:47,320
[Grab your foot.]

773
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:51,480
[Pull your feet upwards diagonally
as far as possible.]

774
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:52,960
[Good.]

775
00:47:56,880 --> 00:47:58,320
[Please hold on for three seconds.]

776
00:47:59,280 --> 00:48:01,080
[You can help each other stretch further.]

777
00:48:01,920 --> 00:48:04,480
[Second time.]

778
00:48:04,480 --> 00:48:06,400
[One more time.]

779
00:48:06,400 --> 00:48:07,880
[Good.]

780
00:48:07,880 --> 00:48:09,320
[One.]

781
00:48:09,320 --> 00:48:12,560
[Lower your leg slowly and take a breath.]

782
00:48:13,160 --> 00:48:15,240
[Exhale.]

783
00:48:15,240 --> 00:48:17,240
[Feeling better?]

784
00:48:17,240 --> 00:48:20,000
[Now let's sit on the mat.]

785
00:48:22,240 --> 00:48:26,000
[We've finished the movement portion]

786
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:27,520
[of our yoga.]

787
00:48:27,520 --> 00:48:29,040
[Next,]

788
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:32,280
[please face each other.]

789
00:48:32,280 --> 00:48:34,680
[How was it?]

790
00:48:34,680 --> 00:48:38,880
[Taichi: Doing it together is easier than]

791
00:48:38,880 --> 00:48:40,640
[Taichi: doing it alone.]

792
00:48:40,640 --> 00:48:43,680
[Taichi: I think we did a good job.]

793
00:48:43,680 --> 00:48:47,560
[Taichi: Syncing our breathing,
we could sorta share our energies.]

794
00:48:47,560 --> 00:48:50,400
[Taichi: That feeling was fascinating.]

795
00:48:50,400 --> 00:48:53,000
[Taichi: It was tiring doing it alone at first.]

796
00:48:53,760 --> 00:48:55,640
[Taichi: It was tough.]

797
00:48:56,160 --> 00:48:58,560
[Taichi: But when we did it together,]

798
00:48:58,560 --> 00:49:00,840
[Taichi: I could push myself further.]

799
00:49:00,840 --> 00:49:03,840
[Taichi: It was cool. What about you?]

800
00:49:03,840 --> 00:49:06,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: It was hard to
find my balance when doing it alone.]

801
00:49:06,760 --> 00:49:10,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: Together, we could
lean on each other and it made it easier.]

802
00:49:10,960 --> 00:49:13,560
[Kim Han Gyeol: I felt more limber]

803
00:49:13,560 --> 00:49:16,480
[Kim Han Gyeol: when doing with him,
since I could lean on him.]

804
00:49:16,480 --> 00:49:18,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: It was fun, and I feel like]

805
00:49:18,680 --> 00:49:20,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: we got closer.]

806
00:49:20,920 --> 00:49:21,960
[Thank you and well done.]

807
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:24,840
[Taichi: Thank you.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you.]

808
00:49:24,840 --> 00:49:27,680
[Taichi: It was fun.]
[That's good to hear.]

809
00:49:27,680 --> 00:49:29,080
[Taichi: The yoga was really fun,]

810
00:49:29,080 --> 00:49:32,720
[Taichi: but I wished the order was different.]

811
00:49:32,720 --> 00:49:35,040
[Taichi: If we had a meal together first,]

812
00:49:35,040 --> 00:49:37,800
[Taichi: and then
did yoga together the next day,]

813
00:49:37,800 --> 00:49:40,280
[Taichi: I'd probably feel different.]

814
00:49:40,280 --> 00:49:43,800
[Taichi: Right now,
I'm not sure about my feelings,]

815
00:49:43,800 --> 00:49:47,160
[Taichi: but I had to
keep maintaining eye contact and stuff.]

816
00:49:47,160 --> 00:49:49,000
[Taichi: I felt like I was just following orders.]

817
00:49:49,000 --> 00:49:51,440
[Taichi: I wasn't at ease,
and couldn't say much too.]

818
00:49:51,440 --> 00:49:53,720
[Taichi: It was really awkward.]

819
00:49:53,720 --> 00:49:55,600
[Taichi: I didn't feel relaxed.]

820
00:49:55,600 --> 00:49:58,160
[Taichi: During yoga too,
whenever the instructor asked how we felt.]

821
00:49:58,160 --> 00:50:01,080
[Taichi: I like to be funny
and make things interesting,]

822
00:50:01,080 --> 00:50:02,720
[Taichi: so I tried to be funny,]

823
00:50:02,720 --> 00:50:06,040
[Taichi: but I think
there wasn't any back and forth between us.]

824
00:50:06,040 --> 00:50:08,160
[Taichi: We weren't on the same wavelength.]

825
00:50:08,160 --> 00:50:11,840
[Taichi: So on the third day,
I became a bit conflicted.]

826
00:50:17,680 --> 00:50:23,120
[Final meditation time]

827
00:50:30,120 --> 00:50:31,920
[Kim Han Gyeol:
To be honest, I wasn't satisfied.]

828
00:50:31,920 --> 00:50:34,160
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't
get close to Taichi that day,]

829
00:50:34,160 --> 00:50:36,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: as compared to
the goal I had in mind.]

830
00:50:36,800 --> 00:50:39,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was drawn to him first, so
I thought the attraction will become stronger.]

831
00:50:39,800 --> 00:50:41,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: But it's just stayed the same.]

832
00:50:41,400 --> 00:50:45,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't discover anything new
about him during the couples yoga too,]

833
00:50:45,440 --> 00:50:49,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: so, hmm... I had some doubts.]

834
00:50:49,960 --> 00:50:54,620
[How will
Han Gyeol and Taichi's relationship pan out?]

835
00:50:54,620 --> 00:51:00,580
[Chuncheon Samaksan
Mountain Lake Cable Car]

836
00:51:00,600 --> 00:51:02,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: The cable car looks fun.]
[Oh Min Seong: Is it your first time?]

837
00:51:03,150 --> 00:51:04,360
It's my first time with a guy.

838
00:51:04,360 --> 00:51:06,960
[Min Seong & Hyeong Jun
are here to ride a cable car]

839
00:51:07,480 --> 00:51:09,200
[I'm scared.]

840
00:51:09,400 --> 00:51:12,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Are you scared of heights?]
[Oh Min Seong: A bit.]

841
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:15,000
[Oh Min Seong: I'm glad
(the floor) isn't transparent.]

842
00:51:15,600 --> 00:51:17,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
Transparent floors are more fun.]

843
00:51:17,680 --> 00:51:21,120
[Oh Min Seong: I'll cry.
My legs will turn into jelly.]

844
00:51:22,560 --> 00:51:23,440
[What?]

845
00:51:23,440 --> 00:51:24,140
[It's transparent.]

846
00:51:24,300 --> 00:51:25,860
[Takes a look]

847
00:51:25,900 --> 00:51:28,560
[Oh Min Seong: Not what I expected.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's shaky.]

848
00:51:29,740 --> 00:51:31,500
[Panics]

849
00:51:31,880 --> 00:51:33,760
[Oh Min Seong: Not what I expected.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I like it.]

850
00:51:33,760 --> 00:51:34,640
[What?]

851
00:51:34,640 --> 00:51:35,720
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I like it.]

852
00:51:41,400 --> 00:51:43,960
[Oh Min Seong: The floor is transparent...]

853
00:51:45,260 --> 00:51:46,260
[Sigh...]

854
00:51:46,500 --> 00:51:48,360
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I guess it's quite high.]

855
00:51:48,360 --> 00:51:50,120
[Oh Min Seong: It looks very high.]

856
00:51:50,840 --> 00:51:52,880
[Oh Min Seong: Although I said (I was scared),]

857
00:51:53,320 --> 00:51:56,560
[Oh Min Seong: I didn't want to
appear scared, so I tried to hide it.]

858
00:51:56,560 --> 00:51:57,880
[Oh Min Seong: To not seem scared...]

859
00:51:58,480 --> 00:52:02,040
[Oh Min Seong: But it's easier said than done.]

860
00:52:02,840 --> 00:52:04,520
[A lot higher than expected for Min Seong]

861
00:52:05,200 --> 00:52:06,840
[Fails to appear cool (?)]

862
00:52:07,340 --> 00:52:08,700
[A glance]

863
00:52:08,920 --> 00:52:12,760
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
He was very scared in the cable car.]

864
00:52:13,400 --> 00:52:16,120
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I saw a lot of his cute moments.]

865
00:52:16,920 --> 00:52:19,680
["So I think i grew fond of him."]

866
00:52:22,440 --> 00:52:26,320
[Oh Min Seong: If only it were sunnier today.]

867
00:52:26,320 --> 00:52:28,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah,
the weather is a bit of a downer.]

868
00:52:30,200 --> 00:52:31,840
[Oh Min Seong: I have a question.]

869
00:52:31,840 --> 00:52:34,320
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What is it?]
[Oh Min Seong: The star gift...]

870
00:52:34,920 --> 00:52:36,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun: The star?]

871
00:52:36,520 --> 00:52:38,520
[Oh Min Seong: Yes,
in the mailbox yesterday... Was it not you?]

872
00:52:39,040 --> 00:52:41,040
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes, it was me.]
[Oh Min Seong: Yes?]

873
00:52:41,100 --> 00:52:41,740
[Shy]

874
00:52:42,320 --> 00:52:44,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I like stars.]

875
00:52:45,320 --> 00:52:50,400
[Oh Min Seong: Why did you
choose me (for today's date)?]

876
00:52:52,360 --> 00:52:55,560
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm curious
about what you're like 1-on-1.]

877
00:52:55,920 --> 00:52:57,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: And Taichi was in the way.]

878
00:52:59,880 --> 00:53:02,480
[In the way...]

879
00:53:03,320 --> 00:53:07,240
[Oh Min Seong: It was a very short date too.]
